{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"当毛主席微笑的时候","authors":["阿列克斯·恰奇"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":10,"day":12}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"当毛主席微笑的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔阿尔巴尼亚〕　阿列克斯·恰奇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当毛主席微笑的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是怎样热爱着人民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地上到处鲜花盛开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野里到处都是丰收。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当毛主席微笑的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民要叫高山低头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人万分害怕东方破晓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们在夜里都睡不好觉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当毛主席微笑的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人也知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的胜利又将出现，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产主义的明天就要来临，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上的乌云即将消散。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当毛主席微笑的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家都知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天的日子会变得更加美好！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}